OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother dry and sunny day,
OL,6,Falthough there is a small chance of
OL,7,Fthe odd shower developing and perhaps
OL,8,Fa few thunderstorms from late
OL,9,Fafternoon. Not as hot but still
OL,10,Ffeeling very warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright and very warm
OL,13,Fevening. Dry for most but an
OL,14,Fincreasing risk of showers moving
OL,15,Facross Wales overnight, these locally
OL,16,Fheavy and thundery in places. Cooler
OL,17,Fthan recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
