OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FDry and bright for most with
OL,6,Fplenty of late spring sunshine. Skies
OL,7,Fturning hazy at times, particularly in
OL,8,Fthe west. Feeling very warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,11,Ffine and settled over the coming days,
OL,12,Fhowever it will turn cloudier from the
OL,13,Fwest at times, perhaps with some
OL,14,Fshowers on Thursday. Temperatures
OL,15,Fslowly returning to normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
